-- Elliott Management reaffirms $3.36 bln bid for Riverbed 
-- 
-- Tue Apr 15, 2014 09:18AM EDT
-- None



April 15 (Reuters) - Hedge fund Elliott Management reaffirmed its $3.36 billion offer for network gear maker Riverbed Technology Inc <RVBD.O>, saying it remained "extremely interested" in acquiring the company.

Riverbed rejected Elliott Management's raised bid in February, saying the offer undervalued the company. [ID:nL3N0LX4PL]